## Disclaimer: You most likely don't need this file
## unless you're running the front separately outside of Docker.
## Use the .env.example file in project root for a template

## Supabase (required for @supabase/ssr integration)
## These match the local Supabase instance started with `supabase start`
## Get the anon key from `supabase status` output
# PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=http://127.0.0.1:54321
# PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=<your-anon-key-from-supabase-status>
